You can attach a few files for test decryption by packing them into an archive with zip, rar, tar, 7zip, 7z, tar.gz extensions of no more than 10 megabytes using the attach button directly in the chat.

If your archive weighs more than 10 megabytes, please use our file sharing service.
http://lockbitfss2w7co3ij6am6wox4xcurtgwukunx3yubcoe5cbxiqakxqd.onion

For security reasons we do not click on other links you send in chat.
Please wait for a reply, sometimes it takes several hours due to possible time zone differences.
Good afternoon, we are interested in recovering our data, how should we proceed?
price for decryption and deleting your data from our servers is  1 BTC.
You can upload a few non-important files to this chat for the test. After payment, you get the tool for ESXI and WINDOWS. Run the tool and your data will be decrypted.
When the timer expires, the decryptor will be deleted and your data will be published

Dear Sir, ISAC is a social organization that cares for the health of the people, with scarce resources and without government help.
1 BTC is completely unrealistic, considering the inflation of our currency against the dollar.
Please carefully consider the possibility of making this concession.
Thank you!
